body_html:
@drpngx The only details I see about the CLA are: "The bad news is that it appears that one or more commits were authored by someone other than the pull request submitter. We need to confirm that they're okay with their commits being contributed to this project. Please have them confirm that here in the pull request."

@sampepose confirmed in this pull request that he's OK with contributing his commit. Are there any further steps necessary? Sam's commit has sampepose@gmail.com which appears to be his email on his profile, and my commits have ringwalt@google.com. I don't see any other commits that got co-mingled.
